<Algorithm code="           1. If _O_ does not have an own property with key _P_, return *undefined*.           1. Let _D_ be a newly created Property Descriptor with no fields.           1. Let _X_ be _O_'s own property whose key is _P_.           1. If _X_ is a data property, then             1. Set _D_.[[Value]] to the value of _X_'s [[Value]] attribute.             1. Set _D_.[[Writable]] to the value of _X_'s [[Writable]] attribute.           1. Else,             1. Assert: _X_ is an accessor property.             1. Set _D_.[[Get]] to the value of _X_'s [[Get]] attribute.             1. Set _D_.[[Set]] to the value of _X_'s [[Set]] attribute.           1. Set _D_.[[Enumerable]] to the value of _X_'s [[Enumerable]] attribute.           1. Set _D_.[[Configurable]] to the value of _X_'s [[Configurable]] attribute.           1. Return _D_.         ">
